:\"AlgoForge is a free, SEO-first coding interview platform with pattern-based learning paths, curated collections (Blind 75, Grind 169), multi-language solutions, and original explanations.\"}</script><header class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-border/80 bg-background/85 backdrop-blur-md\"><div class=\"container-af flex h-14 items-center justify-between gap-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 font-bold tracking-tight\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-primary text-primary-foreground text-xs font-black\">AF</span><span class=\"hidden sm:inline\">AlgoForge</span></a><nav class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-1\" aria-label=\"Main\"><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/topics\">Topics</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/patterns\">Patterns</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/roadmaps\">Roadmaps</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/blind-75\">Blind 75</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/companies\">Companies</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></nav></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"hidden sm:inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:border-primary/40 transition-colors\" href=\"/search\"><span>Search…</span><kbd class=\"rounded border border-border bg-muted px-1.5 text-[10px] font-mono\">/</kbd></a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/dashboard\">Progress</a><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 hover:bg-muted text-foreground h-9 w-9\" aria-label=\"Toggle theme\"></button></div></div></header><main id=\"main\" class=\"min-h-[70vh]\"><div class=\"container-af py-10\"><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Problems\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Minimum Number of Flips to Convert Binary Matrix to Zero Matrix\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/minimum-number-of-flips-to-convert-binary-matrix-to-zero-matrix\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":4,\"name\":\"Python\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/minimum-number-of-flips-to-convert-binary-matrix-to-zero-matrix/python\"}]}</script><ol class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/problems/minimum-number-of-flips-to-convert-binary-matrix-to-zero-matrix\">Minimum Number of Flips to Convert Binary Matrix to Zero Matrix</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><span class=\"text-foreground font-medium\" aria-current=\"page\">Python</span></li></ol></nav><div class=\"mt-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide bg-hard/15 text-hard\">Hard</span></div><h1 class=\"mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Minimum Number of Flips to Convert Binary Matrix to Zero Matrix<!-- --> — <!-- -->Python</h1><p class=\"mt-2 text-muted-foreground\"><a class=\"text-primary hover:underline\" href=\"/problems/minimum-number-of-flips-to-convert-binary-matrix-to-zero-matrix\">Full explanation</a> · <!-- -->Time <!-- -->O((m * n) * 2^(m * n))<!-- --> · Space <!-- -->O((m * n) * 2^(m * n))</p><div class=\"mt-8\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border overflow-hidden bg-code-bg text-slate-100\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 border-b border-white/10 bg-black/30 px-2 py-1.5\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-1\" role=\"tablist\" aria-label=\"Language\"><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium transition-colors text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5\">C++</button><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium transition-colors bg-white/15 text-white\">Python</button></div><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 px-3 text-sm text-slate-300 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/10 h-8\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Copy code\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-copy h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg>Copy</button></div><pre class=\"overflow-x-auto p-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed font-mono max-h-[32rem]\"><code># Time:  O((m * n) * 2^(m * n))\n# Space: O((m * n) * 2^(m * n))\n\nimport collections\n\n\nclass Solution(object):\n    def minFlips(self, mat):\n        &quot;&quot;&quot;\n        :type mat: List[List[int]]\n        :rtype: int\n        &quot;&quot;&quot;\n        directions = [(0, 0), (0, 1), (1, 0), (0, -1), (-1, 0)]\n        start = sum(val &lt;&lt; r*len(mat[0])+c for r, row in enumerate(mat) for c, val in enumerate(row))\n        q = collections.deque([(start, 0)])\n        lookup = {start}\n        while q:\n            state, step = q.popleft()\n            if not state:\n                return step\n            for r in xrange(len(mat)):\n                for c in xrange(len(mat[0])):\n                    new_state = state\n                    for dr, dc in directions:\n                        nr, nc = r+dr, c+dc\n                        if 0 &lt;= nr &lt; len(mat) and 0 &lt;= nc &lt; len(mat[0]):\n                            new_state ^= 1 &lt;&lt; nr*len(mat[0])+nc\n                    if new_state in lookup:\n                        continue\n                    lookup.add(new_state)\n                    q.append((new_state, step+1))\n        return -1\n</code></pre></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"mt-20 border-t border-border bg-sidebar\"><div class=\"container-af py-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><div><p class=\"font-bold text-lg\">AlgoForge</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground max-w-xs\">Master coding interviews with patterns, roadmaps, and solutions</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Learn</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/patterns\">Patterns</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/roadmaps\">Roadmaps</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/blind-75\">Blind 75</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/grind-169\">Grind 169</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Interview</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/companies\">Companies</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/interview-preparation\">Interview prep</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/system-design\">System design</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/glossary\">Glossary</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Product</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/about\">About</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/about/attribution\">Attribution</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/sitemap-html\">Sitemap</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-border\"><div class=\"container-af py-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 justify-between text-xs text-muted-foreground\"><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> <!-- -->AlgoForge<!-- -->. Educational use only.</p><p>Solution code sourced under MIT from<!-- --> <a href=\"https://github.com/kamyu104/LeetCode-Solutions\" class=\"underline hover:text-primary\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">kamyu104/LeetCode-Solutions</a>. Explanations are original AlgoForge content.</p></div></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/05kafvajig4wu.js\" id=\"_